reviewText: I was disappointed with this movie for it was modified from the original version.  When the actors are speaking at several times, their voice becomes mute because they say something that may not be appropriate.  I thought the movie was original and did not require it to have these modifications.  This should have been stated in the description for buyers to know of their modifications.

this is a great movie to watch, full of comedy! it has all the funniest actors to those who know them, Resortes, Carmen Salina, Pedro Infante Jr. and When they are in the dance contest, Resortes one of the best dancer from his time is halerious.
